prompts.frontCover: Flat 2D illustration for a greeting card, dreamy fantasy art style. A charming, cartoon-style capybara is meditating serenely on a giant, fluffy, iridescent dandelion seed head that is floating gently through a magical twilight sky. The capybara has its eyes closed with a blissful, tiny smile. A group of three mischievous, tiny gnomes with pointy red hats are playfully trying to tickle the capybara's feet with long, glowing feathers, but the capybara remains utterly unbothered and in a state of zen. The sky is a soft gradient of lavender and peach, filled with sparkling, bioluminescent motes of light and whimsical, swirling star constellations. Below, a whimsical, rolling landscape of soft, mossy hills can be seen. In the center of the image, written in a beautiful, readable, elegant cursive script made of shimmering gold light, is the text: "Wishing you a day of unbothered bliss. Happy Birthday". The overall aesthetic is humorous, ethereal, and magical.
